    "post_content": "<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Here’s announcing the second call for the SrijanShakti Awards.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Awards, launched in 2024, recognize exceptional female contributors who push the boundaries of design and creativity. These awards celebrate innovation, leadership, and transformative impact across the creative spectrum.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nominations are invited under 3 categories –<br>> Design Entrepreneur of the Year<br>> Industry Innovation Champion &amp;<br>> Social Impact Catalyst</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is your time &amp; send in your nomination now!!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Link for Nomination is - <a href=\"https://forms.gle/UTVqiAuy57hcezddA\">https://forms.gle/UTVqiAuy57hcezddA</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The awards ceremony will be held on International Women's Day, March 11, 2025 at the IIC Seminar Hall, New Delhi</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->",
